About.Name: Henry Moe
About.AboutText: Hello, my name is Henry. I am a fourth year student at Seattle Pacific University pursuing a self-designed major in acoustical engineering. As a lifelong musician, I am interested in the feild of architectural acoustics. I enjoy problem solving and working collaboratively with others. This summer, a will be interning with the acoustical consulting team at Stantec, after which I will return to SPU for one quarter to complete my degree.

Experience.EducationText: I started at Seattle Pacific University as a music student, but became interested in acoustics, so I worked with SPU to design my own major in acoustical engineering that combines my music education with engineering classes. I expect to graduate at the end of 2025.

Project1.Title: AC Filter Design Project
Project1.Desc: As part of the Circuits II class, I designed and built a circuit to filter an AC signal.
